introduction: Health Catalyst and Healthcare AI are initiatives that aim to make machine learning and predictive analytics widely available in healthcare. CatalystAI is a platform that integrates machine learning models into various healthcare products, while HealthcareAI is an open-source repository for machine learning software and expertise. These tools have the potential to improve patient outcomes by allowing caregivers to make predictive analytics routine and actionable. The video discusses the benefits of these technologies and their accessibility, as well as their role in accelerating outcomes improvement in the value-based world of healthcare.
